TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT /*+ Parallel(IN_ST_PREMCSCNT,4)*/ IN_ST_PREMCSCNT.TXT_POLICY_NO, IN_ST_PREMCSCNT.DTE_TXN_DATE, IN_ST_PREMCSCNT.TXT_TXN_CD, IN_ST_PREMCSCNT.DEC_SEQ_NO, IN_ST_PREMCSCNT.TXT_COMP_CD, IN_ST_PREMCSCNT.TXT_RIDER_NO, IN_ST_PREMCSCNT.TXT_COVERAGE_NO, IN_ST_PREMCSCNT.TXT_LIFE_NO, 'Duplicated records were found, total record ' || to_char(count(*)) AS TXT_ERROR_MSG, IN_ST_PREMCSCNT.TXT_FILE_NAME FROM IN_ST_PREMCSCNT WHERE txt_file_name = '$$STR_CONTROL_FILE_NAME' GROUP BY DTE_TXN_DATE, TXT_COMP_CD, TXT_POLICY_NO, IN_ST_PREMCSCNT.TXT_TXN_CD, TXT_LIFE_NO, TXT_COVERAGE_NO, TXT_RIDER_NO, DEC_SEQ_NO, txt_file_name having count(*) > 1

TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: delete from IN_PMTX_DUP_RESULT where txt_file_name = '$$STR_CONTROL_FILE_NAME'; commit;
